WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue(c.color9CD5FF) { color: #9CD5FF; }
::cue(c.colora8c7fa) { color: #a8c7fa; }

1
00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:07.000 line:5% align:middle
<b><c.color9CD5FF>One Pace Premium</c></b>
Keep the project alive: <c.colora8c7fa>ko-fi.com/not6ip</c>

2
00:00:00.310 --> 00:00:03.180
Open up the borderless map, then

3
00:00:03.180 --> 00:00:06.380
Head for that unknown edge of the ocean

4
00:00:06.380 --> 00:00:10.770
LET’S SAIL ON right now, hoist your sails up high

5
00:00:10.770 --> 00:00:13.760
Riding on the wind

6
00:00:18.890 --> 00:00:23.100
DON’T GIVE UP, it’s time to finish what we started

7
00:00:23.290 --> 00:00:26.070
So don't you grow disheartened

8
00:00:26.380 --> 00:00:29.830
Laugh the tears away through the storm

9
00:00:30.030 --> 00:00:34.260
SHOUT IT OUT, when you feel down always remember

10
00:00:34.600 --> 00:00:36.860
That’s what your friends are there for

11
00:00:36.890 --> 00:00:39.020
Y’know there’s no point in fronting,

12
00:00:39.020 --> 00:00:42.940
your crew will always have your back

13
00:00:43.310 --> 00:00:47.040
Even in the face of utter darkness

14
00:00:47.270 --> 00:00:50.030
C’mon, BRAVE IT OUT We’ll be alright

15
00:00:50.330 --> 00:00:53.820
Together you know that we’ll never lose a fight

16
00:00:54.040 --> 00:00:56.810
Open up the borderless map, then

17
00:00:56.830 --> 00:00:59.670
Head for that unknown edge of the ocean

18
00:00:59.970 --> 00:01:04.250
All great journeys starts with a single step

19
00:01:04.320 --> 00:01:05.260
DREAMIN’ ON

20
00:01:05.260 --> 00:01:08.040
Open up the borderless map, then

21
00:01:08.040 --> 00:01:10.780
Raise the flag we swore to defend

22
00:01:10.930 --> 00:01:13.670
We’ll never stop until we’ve reached the top

23
00:01:13.740 --> 00:01:18.140
Just be true to yourself until the end

24
00:01:18.270 --> 00:01:22.980
Set sail and grab it, DREAMIN ON

25
00:01:45.080 --> 00:01:49.630
<b>Retainers of Glory</b>

26
00:01:49.630 --> 00:01:52.840
<b>Rear

Entrance</b>
Sir Kin'emon! Sir Denjiro!

27
00:01:52.840 --> 00:01:54.300
Best of luck!

28
00:01:54.800 --> 00:01:56.310
To you as well!

29
00:02:23.870 --> 00:02:26.420
We have no money, Lord Oden!

30
00:02:26.420 --> 00:02:27.250
Truly?!

31
00:02:27.590 --> 00:02:30.050
We have nothing to eat for supper!

32
00:02:30.050 --> 00:02:32.300
Okay, I have a job for you!

33
00:02:32.300 --> 00:02:34.430
Go to town and beg for food!

34
00:02:34.430 --> 00:02:35.340
Again?!

35
00:02:43.140 --> 00:02:46.580
I am sure it was painful, everyone.

36
00:02:47.970 --> 00:02:48.850
Kin...

37
00:02:52.360 --> 00:02:54.570
For now, let us march on.

38
00:02:55.570 --> 00:02:56.500
Izo...

39
00:03:02.700 --> 00:03:06.420
Have you made peace with perishing here?

40
00:03:06.420 --> 00:03:09.310
I will not miss another chance to die.

41
00:03:12.040 --> 00:03:14.010
Then let us go.

42
00:03:17.800 --> 00:03:18.760
Okiku.

43
00:03:49.670 --> 00:03:53.920
Make your choice, samurai of Orochi!

44
00:03:53.920 --> 00:03:57.840
Do you wanna die alongside
your lord Orochi here?!

45
00:03:58.180 --> 00:04:00.510
Or will you conquer the world with us?!

46
00:04:01.010 --> 00:04:04.800
I'm well aware of how loyal you samurai are.

47
00:04:05.880 --> 00:04:10.560
I admire even those of you who challenge us!

48
00:04:14.020 --> 00:04:19.360
The 5,000 strong Oniwabanshu,
the ninja force of Wano!

49
00:04:19.740 --> 00:04:22.240
Allow us to serve you!

50
00:04:23.030 --> 00:04:26.750
Likewise, the samurai of Wano, 5,000 strong!

51
00:04:27.210 --> 00:04:29.040
Henceforth, we serve you!

52
00:04:31.680 --> 00:04:33.290
Welcome aboard!

53
00:04:38.970 --> 00:04:40.390
Shogun Orochi...

54
00:04:41.470 --> 00:04:42.760
Well, that's that...

55
00:04:44.310 --> 00:04:49.190
Good to hear! I didn't wanna turn coat
and have to kill you guys outta nowhere!

56
00:04:49.530 --> 00:04:51.270
Pleasure workin' with ya!

57
00:04:55.560 --> 00:04:58.070
They have no right to be called samurai!

58
00:04:58.070 --> 00:05:00.280
Hold it in for now, Boss Hyogoro!

59
00:05:04.490 --> 00:05:09.680
To think you actually brought
that worthless shogun's troops to our side...

60
00:05:10.860 --> 00:05:13.540
You're not half bad.

61
00:05:22.440 --> 00:05:26.150
Now our forces are really coming together.

62
00:05:28.270 --> 00:05:29.520
Let me go!

63
00:05:29.520 --> 00:05:32.230
No! Get off me!

64
00:05:32.230 --> 00:05:34.730
Keep them restrained.

65
00:05:39.680 --> 00:05:42.360
I'm not letting you get away with this!

66
00:05:42.360 --> 00:05:45.700
If Shinobu can escape,
we still have a chance!

67
00:05:46.270 --> 00:05:47.990
I'm sorry, Onami!

68
00:05:47.990 --> 00:05:49.370
I must advance!

69
00:05:50.690 --> 00:05:52.500
Hurry and help Momo!

70
00:05:53.980 --> 00:05:56.340
Lord Oden knew!

71
00:05:56.340 --> 00:05:59.050
He knew that felling Orochi
would change nothing!

72
00:05:59.730 --> 00:06:04.390
The only one in need of defeat for
the past twenty years has been Kaido!

73
00:06:13.440 --> 00:06:16.200
As it stands now, within Wano...

74
00:06:16.200 --> 00:06:21.530
there's no shogun or
any samurai serving him!

75
00:06:22.860 --> 00:06:25.240
The unwitting citizens of the Flower Capital...

76
00:06:25.240 --> 00:06:30.410
must be enjoying the festivities too much
to see that this will be their last day.

77
00:06:39.170 --> 00:06:40.670
Hey, brat!

78
00:06:40.670 --> 00:06:43.050
I've had my doubts for a while.

79
00:06:44.180 --> 00:06:46.820
A coward like you...

80
00:06:46.820 --> 00:06:50.860
can't be the son of
a daredevil like Kozuki Oden!

81
00:06:53.350 --> 00:06:54.270
I...

82
00:06:58.110 --> 00:07:04.200
This execution will bring about
an end to the old Wano.

83
00:07:04.710 --> 00:07:07.870
Looking back on that day twenty years ago...

84
00:07:07.870 --> 00:07:10.740
inside that burning castle...

85
00:07:12.620 --> 00:07:16.040
you never answered my question!

86
00:07:20.830 --> 00:07:23.260
Please... save me...!

87
00:07:26.880 --> 00:07:29.470
What is your name?

88
00:07:29.470 --> 00:07:30.850
Answer!

89
00:07:35.140 --> 00:07:36.480
Father!

90
00:07:37.100 --> 00:07:39.970
Somebody, help me!

91
00:07:48.210 --> 00:07:53.030
If you aren't the son
of Kozuki Oden and Toki,

92
00:07:53.030 --> 00:07:55.910
I'll call off the execution immediately.

93
00:07:56.690 --> 00:08:00.750
After all, such a false accusation
would tarnish my reputation.

94
00:08:05.460 --> 00:08:09.390
However, if you still insist
on calling yourself their son...

95
00:08:10.180 --> 00:08:14.850
you'll face the same fate Oden did.

96
00:08:21.440 --> 00:08:24.160
I'll ask you one more time, brat.

97
00:08:25.780 --> 00:08:28.320
What is your name?!

98
00:08:28.320 --> 00:08:30.780
Viceroy Kaido is so generous!

99
00:08:30.780 --> 00:08:35.590
All the rugrat has to do is lie
and he gets to live!

100
00:08:37.040 --> 00:08:40.750
Think up a good name, kiddo!

101
00:08:44.920 --> 00:08:48.800
Even if you have to lie,
please choose to survive!

102
00:08:49.180 --> 00:08:51.040
Lord Momonosuke!

103
00:08:58.020 --> 00:09:00.140
What?! Then that boy...

104
00:09:00.850 --> 00:09:03.730
is the real Kozuki Momonosuke?!

105
00:09:03.730 --> 00:09:04.980
That's right!

106
00:09:04.980 --> 00:09:07.610
Oden's retainers are all alive!

107
00:09:08.650 --> 00:09:09.780
What?!

108
00:09:13.660 --> 00:09:15.790
Intruders!

109
00:09:19.960 --> 00:09:22.330
Outta my way!

110
00:09:26.960 --> 00:09:32.180
If all the Red Scabbards samurai
I saw that day are...

111
00:09:34.930 --> 00:09:38.220
If they're all alive, then that's wonderful!

112
00:09:38.220 --> 00:09:40.480
Just wonderful!

113
00:09:40.900 --> 00:09:43.020
I can hardly believe it!

114
00:09:44.060 --> 00:09:45.770
Momonosuke is waiting for you!

115
00:09:47.070 --> 00:09:48.360
Let's hurry!

116
00:09:48.360 --> 00:09:51.590
The Nine Red Scabbards are here, right?!

117
00:09:51.590 --> 00:09:53.880
Lemme go, Yamabro!

118
00:09:54.780 --> 00:09:57.080
Yamabro? Why are you calling me that?

119
00:09:57.080 --> 00:10:00.220
Please stop, Young Master Yamato!

120
00:10:01.290 --> 00:10:02.780
Stop!

121
00:10:02.780 --> 00:10:06.090
Young Master Yamato and Straw Hat Luffy
are heading your way!

122
00:10:06.420 --> 00:10:08.210
To the Performance Floor?

123
00:10:08.210 --> 00:10:11.030
Yes! We'll catch them!

124
00:10:11.030 --> 00:10:12.300
Don't bother.

125
00:10:12.300 --> 00:10:13.680
You're no match–

126
00:10:15.690 --> 00:10:17.890
They dare to mess with my men?!

127
00:10:18.760 --> 00:10:21.180
Yamato!

128
00:10:21.180 --> 00:10:23.390
You're gonna pay for this!

129
00:10:30.030 --> 00:10:32.650
No way! Usopp, not over here!

130
00:10:32.650 --> 00:10:35.030
It looks dangerous!

131
00:10:35.240 --> 00:10:38.490
You heard the broadcast earlier!

132
00:10:38.490 --> 00:10:40.260
They're gonna kill Momo!

133
00:10:41.990 --> 00:10:43.120
The giants!

134
00:10:44.180 --> 00:10:46.670
They'll gobble us up!

135
00:10:46.670 --> 00:10:48.340
Turn around, Usopp!

136
00:10:48.340 --> 00:10:50.210
Stow your fears, Chopper!

137
00:10:50.210 --> 00:10:52.920
We fought an Emperor to a standstill!

138
00:10:53.470 --> 00:10:57.890
Believe in the General Franky! It was
tough enough to withstand Big Mom's attacks!

139
00:10:57.890 --> 00:10:59.350
I can't!

140
00:10:59.350 --> 00:11:01.600
I can't handle these monsters!

141
00:11:01.600 --> 00:11:03.180
Never give up!

142
00:11:03.180 --> 00:11:04.890
Never surrender!

143
00:11:04.890 --> 00:11:07.800
Tank Commander Chopper,
what are your orders?!

144
00:11:11.070 --> 00:11:12.860
Retreat! Retreat!

145
00:11:20.450 --> 00:11:22.040
Are you scared?!

146
00:11:23.830 --> 00:11:25.460
Cut the "samurai" crap!

147
00:11:25.460 --> 00:11:28.830
I'm gonna be King of the Pirates someday!

148
00:11:31.550 --> 00:11:33.920
Because your father is a great man...

149
00:11:33.920 --> 00:11:38.780
and you will one day carry
this nation on your shoulders.

150
00:11:49.480 --> 00:11:51.600
The meaning of your name?

151
00:11:51.600 --> 00:11:52.270
Yes!

152
00:11:54.860 --> 00:12:00.370
I want you to grow into a compassionate,
open-minded, and admirable man.

153
00:12:04.790 --> 00:12:05.660
Momo!

154
00:12:07.500 --> 00:12:08.750
Momo...

155
00:12:08.750 --> 00:12:12.350
means peerless!

156
00:12:13.710 --> 00:12:15.420
My name is...

157
00:12:15.420 --> 00:12:18.340
Kozuki Momonosuke!

158
00:12:18.800 --> 00:12:22.550
One day, I will become...

159
00:12:22.550 --> 00:12:29.020
the shogun of Wano!

160
00:12:34.020 --> 00:12:35.650
Lord Momonosuke!

161
00:12:37.610 --> 00:12:41.320
I swear I will save you no matter
the cost, Lord Momonosuke!

162
00:12:43.120 --> 00:12:45.950
Well said, Momonosuke!

163
00:12:45.950 --> 00:12:47.200
We're almost there, Luffy!

164
00:12:49.670 --> 00:12:51.380
Let me take these off!

165
00:12:51.380 --> 00:12:52.670
I promised you!

166
00:12:52.670 --> 00:12:53.700
If you would!

167
00:12:55.460 --> 00:12:58.070
However, just to be safe...

168
00:12:58.090 --> 00:12:59.630
please throw them far away.

169
00:13:00.190 --> 00:13:03.280
Although, I doubt they'll explode...

170
00:13:13.230 --> 00:13:16.610
Is Wano filled with only halfwits?!

171
00:13:24.540 --> 00:13:27.330
Father... Mother...

172
00:13:27.890 --> 00:13:30.750
I merely wished to be a man...

173
00:13:31.420 --> 00:13:36.980
who would be free of shame when
next he sees you in the afterlife.

174
00:13:37.960 --> 00:13:41.880
Hiyori, I wish I could see you again,
even if for a moment...

175
00:13:41.880 --> 00:13:44.340
I do not want to die!

176
00:13:44.340 --> 00:13:46.780
I do not want to cry!

177
00:13:46.780 --> 00:13:49.560
A samurai should not cry in front of others...

178
00:13:49.970 --> 00:13:51.960
How shameful...

179
00:14:02.360 --> 00:14:03.410
They came off!

180
00:14:06.240 --> 00:14:09.120
Hot, hot, hot, hot, hot!

181
00:14:09.120 --> 00:14:10.160
Wh–

182
00:14:10.160 --> 00:14:11.410
Luffy?!

183
00:14:11.830 --> 00:14:14.000
Dammit!

184
00:14:14.000 --> 00:14:17.750
That freaking cowrilla!

185
00:14:18.800 --> 00:14:22.930
He was going to kill me!

186
00:14:23.270 --> 00:14:25.840
What was that explosion?!

187
00:14:25.840 --> 00:14:27.760
Go find out, pronto!

188
00:14:35.440 --> 00:14:37.610
Now it's clear to me.

189
00:14:37.610 --> 00:14:41.190
That man is no longer my father!

190
00:14:43.030 --> 00:14:46.570
Was this your doing, you spoiled brat?!

191
00:14:56.460 --> 00:14:57.710
Hold on, Yamabro!

192
00:14:58.460 --> 00:15:00.880
You stupid old man!

193
00:15:06.590 --> 00:15:08.600
We made it just in time...

194
00:15:08.600 --> 00:15:11.470
but it's not gonna be me or Yamabro.

195
00:15:18.060 --> 00:15:22.280
We're not the ones who'll start this battle!

196
00:16:33.540 --> 00:16:35.060
The Red Scabbards!

197
00:16:35.060 --> 00:16:36.680
Where did they come from?!

198
00:16:41.900 --> 00:16:43.690
The rulers of the minks?!

199
00:16:43.690 --> 00:16:45.440
They're alive!

200
00:16:48.880 --> 00:16:51.320
You damn ghosts!
Prepare for my counterattack!

201
00:16:56.440 --> 00:16:57.580
Izo!

202
00:17:00.080 --> 00:17:02.210
Hey, dumbasses!

203
00:17:02.210 --> 00:17:04.380
Quit drinking already!

204
00:17:05.130 --> 00:17:07.010
Go grab your weapons!

205
00:17:07.010 --> 00:17:09.550
It's a raid!

206
00:17:10.970 --> 00:17:12.050
Are you...

207
00:17:12.050 --> 00:17:14.050
Kyoshiro?!

208
00:17:15.060 --> 00:17:16.630
Kaido!

209
00:17:19.940 --> 00:17:22.350
You half-ghost bastards!

210
00:17:28.270 --> 00:17:30.320
Surrender Name And Thoughts...

211
00:17:30.990 --> 00:17:33.780
Calm all Hesitation!

212
00:17:33.780 --> 00:17:36.540
Your blades...

213
00:17:36.540 --> 00:17:39.150
cannot cut me!

214
00:17:46.420 --> 00:17:49.510
Stake your lives on this blow!

215
00:17:52.090 --> 00:17:53.800
Oden!

216
00:17:53.800 --> 00:17:58.050
Never set foot in Wano again!

217
00:18:11.900 --> 00:18:14.740
SNATCH!

218
00:18:35.430 --> 00:18:38.310
Oden Two-Sword Style:

219
00:18:38.660 --> 00:18:41.020
Halcyon Totsuka!

220
00:18:43.100 --> 00:18:43.230
<b>Hal</b>

221
00:18:43.230 --> 00:18:43.350
<b>Halcyon</b>

222
00:18:43.350 --> 00:18:43.480
<b>Halcyon</b>
<b>Tot</b>

223
00:18:43.480 --> 00:18:43.560
<b>Halcyon</b>
<b>Totsuka</b>

224
00:18:48.760 --> 00:18:51.230
The scar Oden left me with...

225
00:18:52.240 --> 00:18:53.900
Why does it hurt?

226
00:18:53.900 --> 00:18:57.280
How do these blades pierce my body?!

227
00:18:57.780 --> 00:19:01.120
Do not underestimate my samurai!

228
00:19:01.120 --> 00:19:03.750
They can forget me...

229
00:19:05.580 --> 00:19:08.170
for all I care...

230
00:19:08.170 --> 00:19:09.620
but...

231
00:19:14.340 --> 00:19:18.300
my spirit will live on!

232
00:19:27.680 --> 00:19:32.360
Are they using Oden's ryuo?!

233
00:19:35.820 --> 00:19:38.660
Pierce through!

234
00:20:05.980 --> 00:20:08.490
They really are Oden's retainers!

235
00:20:08.490 --> 00:20:10.690
They sure are strong!

236
00:20:11.980 --> 00:20:14.440
Quite the deadly banquet!

237
00:20:15.200 --> 00:20:17.450
Did Kaido kick the bucket?

238
00:20:17.450 --> 00:20:19.070
Fight back!

239
00:20:19.070 --> 00:20:21.620
Kill those Red Scabbard rats!

240
00:20:24.450 --> 00:20:29.710
So Straw Hat, Kid, and all the others were
merely distractions for this ambush?!

241
00:20:29.710 --> 00:20:31.880
Stay alert, you guys!

242
00:20:31.880 --> 00:20:35.130
There could still be intruders around here!

243
00:20:35.130 --> 00:20:37.010
Spot on!

244
00:21:10.540 --> 00:21:12.670
Open your ears, weaklings!

245
00:21:13.040 --> 00:21:16.380
We won't let you bring harm
to Kin'emon and his samurai!

246
00:21:16.380 --> 00:21:19.050
Alright! Let's get in on this!

247
00:21:19.050 --> 00:21:21.130
We'll give Kaido another beating!

248
00:21:21.130 --> 00:21:22.590
There you are!

249
00:21:24.010 --> 00:21:25.760
Yamato!

250
00:21:27.890 --> 00:21:28.810
Headbutt!

251
00:21:32.440 --> 00:21:33.440
Ulti!

252
00:21:39.740 --> 00:21:42.280
The nerve, striking me as you did!

253
00:21:42.280 --> 00:21:44.780
I am on your side,
yet you brutally assaulted me,

254
00:21:44.780 --> 00:21:48.290
and now you're running around
the place with that Straw Hat...

255
00:21:48.290 --> 00:21:50.250
Whatever are you doing?!

256
00:21:51.580 --> 00:21:53.830
Nothing to get upset over.

257
00:21:53.830 --> 00:21:57.670
The day that I become
Kozuki Oden is finally here!

258
00:21:59.090 --> 00:22:02.430
What are you talking about?! Are you crazy?!

259
00:22:04.140 --> 00:22:06.850
Young Master Yamato, we have a problem!

260
00:22:06.850 --> 00:22:09.100
Your father was just attacked,

261
00:22:09.100 --> 00:22:12.470
and now the floor is swarming with enemies!

262
00:22:12.470 --> 00:22:14.600
Please stop fooling around!

263
00:22:14.600 --> 00:22:15.650
I'm well aware!

264
00:22:15.650 --> 00:22:21.030
I'm not your ally anymore,
and I don't give a damn if my father dies!

265
00:22:21.030 --> 00:22:22.530
– What?!
– What?!

266
00:22:22.940 --> 00:22:24.820
What is it this time?

267
00:22:24.820 --> 00:22:27.950
This banquet is getting far too rowdy...

268
00:22:27.950 --> 00:22:30.330
Gum-Gum...

269
00:22:31.370 --> 00:22:34.500
Elephant Gun!

270
00:22:36.590 --> 00:22:37.920
That boy...

271
00:22:51.890 --> 00:22:52.980
Oh crap!

272
00:22:52.980 --> 00:22:54.480
She saw Luffy!

273
00:23:05.610 --> 00:23:07.030
Big Mom!

274
00:23:07.030 --> 00:23:08.910
But I'm busy right now!

275
00:23:10.790 --> 00:23:12.910
I finally found you...

276
00:23:12.910 --> 00:23:17.380
Straw Hat!

277
00:23:29.550 --> 00:23:31.390
Ulti...

278
00:23:33.290 --> 00:23:34.480
Mortar!

279
00:23:46.610 --> 00:23:48.620
Carrot! Let's make a break for it!

280
00:23:49.700 --> 00:23:50.910
Got it!

281
00:23:53.500 --> 00:23:54.910
Better get ready!

282
00:23:56.670 --> 00:23:58.260
Black Ball!

283
00:24:02.750 --> 00:24:04.880
Hey, are you okay?!

284
00:24:05.420 --> 00:24:07.380
Here goes!

285
00:24:07.380 --> 00:24:09.590
Same here!

286
00:24:09.590 --> 00:24:11.810
Thundercloud Rod!

287
00:24:17.520 --> 00:24:19.060
Eleclaw!

288
00:24:24.530 --> 00:24:27.740
Ninpo: Ectoplasm Thunder!

289
00:24:45.510 --> 00:24:46.630
We did it!

290
00:24:50.840 --> 00:24:56.770
You came into my territory
and disgraced my crew!

291
00:24:58.890 --> 00:25:03.770
So I came all the way from
Totto Land to kill you!

292
00:25:04.990 --> 00:25:07.360
Straw Hat!

293
00:25:09.490 --> 00:25:12.240
Why are you here?

294
00:25:12.240 --> 00:25:18.080
And don't tell me it's to take down Kaido,
because that'd be too damn rich.

295
00:25:18.080 --> 00:25:20.170
It's not that!

296
00:25:20.170 --> 00:25:21.330
What?

297
00:25:22.960 --> 00:25:23.750
Luffy?!

298
00:25:28.970 --> 00:25:31.630
What do you mean, Sir Straw Hat?!

299
00:25:31.630 --> 00:25:33.770
It's not, Luffy?!

300
00:25:35.350 --> 00:25:36.470
No!

301
00:25:36.470 --> 00:25:37.680
I'm...

302
00:25:41.480 --> 00:25:43.900
After twenty years,

303
00:25:43.900 --> 00:25:47.190
the Red Scabbards samurai
will come to get their revenge...

304
00:25:47.750 --> 00:25:53.030
Nobody believed Orochi's delusions,
but it would seem they're coming to pass.

305
00:25:56.950 --> 00:26:00.460
I can't believe you made
common cause with pirates.

306
00:26:00.460 --> 00:26:05.340
The rumor about the shadows
at the ruins of Oden Castle...

307
00:26:05.340 --> 00:26:07.340
Punk Hazard.

308
00:26:07.340 --> 00:26:09.090
Dressrosa.

309
00:26:09.090 --> 00:26:11.590
The phantom island Zou.

310
00:26:11.590 --> 00:26:16.140
And the crew behind it all,
the Straw Hat Pirates!

311
00:26:16.850 --> 00:26:18.850
By some curious coincidence,

312
00:26:18.850 --> 00:26:24.310
you people were hiding in the shadows
of my enemies, the Straw Hats.

313
00:26:24.310 --> 00:26:29.570
Some of you held out for twenty years,
while others jumped ahead and ran about,

314
00:26:29.570 --> 00:26:32.360
and just like that, your troops were gathered.

315
00:26:33.780 --> 00:26:37.990
But pirates will stab you in the back!

316
00:26:39.240 --> 00:26:43.340
The moment they sense defeat,
they'll abandon you and run.

317
00:26:43.340 --> 00:26:49.380
I've already taken Straw Hat Luffy out once!

318
00:26:50.550 --> 00:26:53.420
You slander the man!

319
00:26:54.880 --> 00:26:57.720
Sir Luffy and your band
could not be more different!

320
00:26:58.390 --> 00:27:02.390
You, Kaido, the officers, Orochi,
and every last person under them!

321
00:27:02.390 --> 00:27:05.770
I'm here to kick all your asses!

322
00:27:06.440 --> 00:27:10.780
He is the man who will stand
at the pinnacle of the sea someday!

323
00:27:10.780 --> 00:27:14.470
Even if we die, he shall live on!

324
00:27:14.470 --> 00:27:17.660
Wano will see daybreak once more!

325
00:27:17.660 --> 00:27:19.160
Because...

326
00:27:19.910 --> 00:27:22.450
such was the promise we made to our lord!

327
00:27:24.790 --> 00:27:27.790
It's gonna be an all-out war!

328
00:27:31.050 --> 00:27:33.790
Don't push your luck.

329
00:27:33.790 --> 00:27:36.760
You only have a few hundred troops!

330
00:27:43.980 --> 00:27:46.100
She's right, numbskulls.

331
00:27:52.070 --> 00:27:52.900
What?

332
00:27:52.900 --> 00:27:54.780
It's an emergency!

333
00:27:54.780 --> 00:27:57.990
Thousands of intruders
are entering from the rear!

334
00:27:59.820 --> 00:28:01.200
What?!

335
00:28:01.200 --> 00:28:04.830
How's that possible?!

336
00:28:08.580 --> 00:28:10.080
Let's go!

337
00:28:17.180 --> 00:28:18.430
Fine!

338
00:28:18.430 --> 00:28:19.970
If you want it so bad...

339
00:28:28.270 --> 00:28:30.230
I'll cut you up as much as you like.

340
00:28:30.230 --> 00:28:31.270
Screw you!

341
00:28:31.570 --> 00:28:32.690
Exactly...

342
00:28:32.690 --> 00:28:34.360
Right back at you!

343
00:28:36.060 --> 00:28:37.340
But why...?!

344
00:28:38.780 --> 00:28:40.160
A samurai...

345
00:28:46.040 --> 00:28:49.170
Sir Zorojuro! We are by your side!

346
00:28:49.170 --> 00:28:50.880
This is Point C!

347
00:28:50.880 --> 00:28:53.500
It's all the samurai we caught
in the Flower Capital...

348
00:28:53.500 --> 00:28:55.300
and the prisoners from Udon!

349
00:28:55.300 --> 00:28:56.760
What the hell is happening?!

350
00:29:09.310 --> 00:29:11.150
Punk...

351
00:29:11.600 --> 00:29:13.020
Gibson!

352
00:29:25.740 --> 00:29:29.090
Don't fall behind, boys!

353
00:29:32.040 --> 00:29:36.000
Thank you for clearing the way for us this far.

354
00:29:36.310 --> 00:29:38.260
Keep your thanks.

355
00:29:38.260 --> 00:29:41.510
I'm only here to take Kaido's head.

356
00:29:41.980 --> 00:29:45.600
Get in my way, and I'll take yours too.

357
00:29:46.010 --> 00:29:47.700
Appreciate the warning.

358
00:29:49.140 --> 00:29:50.350
Room!

359
00:29:52.980 --> 00:29:54.230
Go to hell!

360
00:29:55.820 --> 00:29:56.900
Amputate!

361
00:29:58.860 --> 00:30:00.070
Shambles!

362
00:30:00.780 --> 00:30:01.570
What?

363
00:30:11.540 --> 00:30:14.630
The pirates that Sir Kin'emon brought...

364
00:30:14.630 --> 00:30:16.840
are pretty damn strong!

365
00:30:17.550 --> 00:30:20.420
How did this all happen?!

366
00:30:20.420 --> 00:30:22.930
A former Warlord, Law, has arrived as well.

367
00:30:22.930 --> 00:30:26.350
They're all working together and gaining power!

368
00:30:26.350 --> 00:30:27.760
Say what?!

369
00:30:27.760 --> 00:30:28.810
Your Awesomeness!

370
00:30:28.810 --> 00:30:30.480
There's more?!

371
00:30:30.480 --> 00:30:32.890
At the entrance of the island,

372
00:30:32.890 --> 00:30:35.770
Marco the Phoenix
and Perospero are working together–

373
00:30:37.860 --> 00:30:40.400
Hey! What happened?!

374
00:30:40.400 --> 00:30:41.990
Hello?!

375
00:30:44.950 --> 00:30:46.700
Candy Maiden!

376
00:30:50.700 --> 00:30:52.410
What's going on?!

377
00:30:52.410 --> 00:30:54.500
Why are they teaming up?!

378
00:31:00.340 --> 00:31:04.010
And now begins the ogre extermination.

379
00:31:04.010 --> 00:31:11.140
I'll turn every last lickety-one of
the Beast Pirates into candy men.

380
00:31:15.810 --> 00:31:18.610
Attention, drunkards of Onigashima!

381
00:31:18.980 --> 00:31:21.070
Tonight's banquet is canceled!

382
00:31:21.810 --> 00:31:23.280
Go grab your weapons!

383
00:31:23.280 --> 00:31:25.910
It's an enemy raid!

384
00:31:33.790 --> 00:31:35.580
Everyone...

385
00:31:39.540 --> 00:31:44.300
Kaido may be gone, but there are
still three Superstars present.

386
00:31:45.070 --> 00:31:47.260
I'm sure there will be a chance!

387
00:31:47.890 --> 00:31:49.680
Lord Momonosuke!

388
00:31:49.680 --> 00:31:52.490
Please wait just a little longer...

389
00:31:53.720 --> 00:31:55.640
Let's do this!

390
00:31:55.640 --> 00:31:58.350
We will take back Wano!

391
00:32:25.130 --> 00:32:28.210
I heard that, Straw Hat!

392
00:32:28.210 --> 00:32:31.010
You say you'll kick my ass?

393
00:32:31.010 --> 00:32:33.180
Then go ahead and try!

394
00:32:33.180 --> 00:32:35.640
I accept your challenge!

395
00:32:42.850 --> 00:32:47.070
I'll show you the world's greatest army!

396
00:33:07.760 --> 00:33:09.090
Sir Luffy!

397
00:33:16.720 --> 00:33:18.180
Many thanks!

398
00:33:18.520 --> 00:33:21.100
Kin'emon! I'll catch up later!

399
00:33:23.980 --> 00:33:25.440
Kaido...

400
00:33:48.690 --> 00:33:52.760
I've completely sobered up.

401
00:33:53.160 --> 00:33:57.180
If it's a fight to the death you want,
it's best out in the open.

402
00:33:57.180 --> 00:34:00.410
Just like that day...

403
00:34:00.410 --> 00:34:04.900
But unlike that day, Oden's already dead.

404
00:34:04.900 --> 00:34:08.100
There's one more difference from that day.

405
00:34:08.100 --> 00:34:10.860
We deduced that when you turn into a dragon,

406
00:34:10.860 --> 00:34:14.820
you wouldn't be able to fight in the dome.

407
00:34:22.620 --> 00:34:26.880
You can't understand
how I've longed for this day!

408
00:34:26.880 --> 00:34:31.050
You will know our rage
when we beat it into you!

409
00:34:31.050 --> 00:34:33.030
The minks...

410
00:34:33.030 --> 00:34:36.930
We brought the warriors from our kingdom.

411
00:34:43.350 --> 00:34:45.690
A flurry of snow in the clear sky...

412
00:34:46.360 --> 00:34:50.110
Perfect for watching the full moon.
